HWREG(1) - User Commands

NAME
      hwreg - Register HW devices

SYNOPSIS
      hwreg slot type

DESCRIPTION
      Registers a hardware device of the given kind in the given slot.

      Type can be one of:
      * raw - allows user space access to associated pins
      * sdcardreader - for SPI based SD card readers
      * dht22 - for DHT22 temperature and humidity sensors
      * atwinc1500 - for ATWINC1500 wireless module

      Slot should be in the range 0-3.
